highlights.text: “Finesse - Remix; feat. Cardi B” by Bruno Mars and Cardi B is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #6.
“Say You Won't Let Go” by James Arthur has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 55 weeks straight.
“A Million Dreams” by Ziv Zaifman, Hugh Jackman, and Michelle Williams is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 93 spots at #99.
Ed Sheeran has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “River (feat. Ed Sheeran)” is the highest at #3.
